<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2177] [PATCH] IndexOutOfBoundsException reading embedded OpenType font</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2177</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;java -jar ~/pdf-box-svn/app/target/pdfbox-app-2.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar PDFToImage opentype.pdf &lt;br/&gt;
PDFToImage failed with the following exception:&lt;br/&gt;
java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException: Index: 2, Size: 2&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.util.SubList.rangeCheck(AbstractList.java:755)&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.util.SubList.get(AbstractList.java:639)&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.util.Collections$SynchronizedList.get(Collections.java:2477)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.fontbox.cff.Type2CharString.drawCurve(Type2CharString.java:356)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;7zip attachment&lt;/p&gt;</description>
